<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1175.107636.figures43-45>
    dc:description "Figures 43 - 45. Synuchus nitidus reticulatus Lindroth, 1956 43 habitus and labels of holotype of Tritrichis chinensis Jedlicka, 1962 44, 45 a non-type male specimens from Guizhou, China 44 habitus 45 male genitalia, left lateral view and dorsal view of median lobe of aedeagus. Scale bars: 2 mm (43, 44); 0.5 mm (45)." ;
